snippet.title: Lemmings (PSX) - 01 - Fun Levels (Part 1 of 2)
snippet.description: Here's the first part of the Fun levels for Lemmings for the Playstation. I'll be showing the Fun levels from every console port I have. No full playthrough for the first Lemmings has been planned yet.
